OL,3,CMan, 26, denies hit-and-run murder in
OL,4,CWolverhampton
OL,6,FA man has denied murdering a 29-year-
OL,7,Fold who was fatally injured in a hit-
OL,8,Fand-run incident.
OL,10,FRyan Griffiths died after he was
OL,11,F"struck" by a car just before 9pm on
OL,12,FAugust 21 which was driven away from
OL,13,Fthe scene in Burleigh Road,
OL,14,FWolverhampton, West Midlands Police
OL,15,Fsaid.
