OL,3,CMan, 26, denies hit-and-run murder in
OL,4,CWolverhampton
OL,6,FAden Wright, 26, pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Fthe charge of murder at Wolverhampton
OL,8,FCrown Court on Tuesday and was
OL,9,Fremanded in custody by Judge Michael
OL,10,FChambers KC before he faces trial on
OL,11,FFebruary 17 at the same court.
OL,13,FWright, of Griffiths Drive in
OL,14,FWolverhampton, spoke only to confirm
OL,15,Fhis name and enter his plea in the
OL,16,Fdock during the short hearing.
OL,18,FThe judge told the court the trial is
OL,19,Fexpected to last two weeks.
