OL,6,FIn a statement released by police days
OL,7,Fafter Mr Griffiths's death, his family
OL,8,Fpaid tribute to him as a "loving and
OL,9,Fdevoted son, brother, uncle, grandson,
OL,10,Fnephew and cousin".
OL,12,FThey added: "Everyone is devastated by
OL,13,Fhis sad loss and he will be sadly
OL,14,Fmissed."
